login the server
> sudo adduser swati 
> sudo adduser swati sudo
> sudo su -
> su - swati
> mkdir .ssh/
> cd .ssh/
> vi authorized_keys
>ls
> exit


change the hostename
> sudo vi /etc/hostname
> sudo reboot

file permisssion
chmod 700 .ssh
chmod 600 .ssh/authorized_keys


for accessing the server
> ssh -A username@bastionIP
> ssh @serverIP

